{"word":"G5227 - ὑπεναντίος - hypenantíos - hoop-en-an-tee'-os - Adversary","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπεναντίος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypenantíos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-en-an-tee'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Adversary</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"எதிரிடையான, எதிர்பார்த்தல் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. opposite to; set over against"},{"paragraph":"2. opposed to, contrary to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G1727 - ἐναντίος - enantíos - en-an-tee'-os/1727\">G1727</a>; <i>under</i> (<i>covertly</i>) <i>contrary</i> to, that is, <i>opposed</i> or (as noun) an <i>opponent:</i> - adversary, against.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}